Banking Details\n</td>\n<td>{{data.deviceId}}</td>\n            </tr>\n        \n        </table>\n        \n        <h3>SCHEDULE III</h3>\n        <p>Additional Terms and Conditions for Personal Loan Agreement in addition to the terms and conditions contained in the Personal Loan agreement and other loan documents the following terms and conditions shall be applicable for the loan applied/ availed by the Borrower. Terms used but not defined herein shall have the meanings ascribed to them in the Agreement or the Loan Document, as the case may be. No extra fee will be charged on pre-payment.</p>\n        <p>Conditions for Pre-Payment:</p>\n        <p>1. Pre-Payment can be done any time after disbursement.</p>\n        <p>2. Subvention would be borne by the merchant.</p>\n        <p>3. Part prepayment is not allowed.</p>\n        <p><b>RECEIVED, READ AND UNDERSTOOD</b></p>\n        <p>Name of the Applicant: {{data.deviceId}}</p>\n        <p>Date: {{data.deviceId}}</p>\n        <p>Place: {{data.deviceId}}</p>\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td>1</td>\n                <td>Name of the 1st Reference of the applicant</td>\n                <td>NA</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>2</td>\n                <td>Relationship of the 1st Reference with the applicant</td>\n                <td>NA</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>3</td>\n                <td>Contact No. of 1st Reference of the applicant</td>\n                <td>NA</td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Optional JavaScript -->\n    <!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->\n    <script src=\"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js\" integrity=\"sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js\" integrity=\"sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv